  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">An Education for over 400 Children in Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fountain of Hope Association offers a home for boys living on the streets in Lusaka, Zambia, in addition to health care and an education for children living in poverty. The organization has very few school supplies and is unable to pay its teachers. As a result, the teachers often do not arrive at work and the students are unable to learn. With additional funds, Fountain of Hope could provide a salary to its teachers, ensuring their attendance, and provide pencils, desks, and other supplies.</narrative>
  </description>
